Class AbstractAdapterItem<DataType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mrapp.android.adapter.datastructure.AbstractAdapterItem<DataType>
  • Type Parameters:
    DataType - The type of the item's data
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable, DataStructure, Filterable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<AbstractAdapterItem<DataType>>

    Group, Item

    public abstract class AbstractAdapterItem<DataType>
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataStructure, android.os.Parcelable, java.lang.Comparable<AbstractAdapterItem<DataType>>, Filterable
    An abstract base class for all data structure, which holds the data of an item of an adapter.
